<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 15:31:11 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1ef73cda07e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;侏儒䴓帮助喂养雏鸟&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Four adult pygmy nuthatches gathered around a nest hole in a dead pine tree" height="768" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/bendur/6a1ef73cda07e.jpg" width="1024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://bendur.some.pics"&gt;@bendur&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 15:31:11 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1ef68c630e3</link><description>&lt;p&gt;2026年4月在我后院看到的一只北方鹪鹩&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A northern house wren stands on a wooden deck railing on a sunny day" height="724" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/bendur/6a1ef68c630e3.jpg" width="1086"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://bendur.some.pics"&gt;@bendur&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 15:28:14 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>六月</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1eb591e558f</link><description>&lt;p&gt;六月&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="June calendar page. This time, the image shows a close-up of a transparent pill box, divided into breakfast, lunch, dinner and bedtime. Behind it lies a Leatherman. The image is in black and white. Surrounding the image is the following poem in German:

Chronisch 
kreisen Gedanken
wabern wandern wirren 
Sorgen Fetzen Emotionen
ungehalten 
ihre Bahnen 
bauen bauschen bäumen
sich auf
ziehen zupfen zerren
ohne Unterlass 
kein 
verlassen ablassen loslassen
rauslassen!

Einhalt bieten 
brechen binden bündeln 
in Bildern Worten Melodien 
frei
gestalten | machen | sein.
Chronisch kreativ

Translated into English: 

Chronically 
thoughts circle
waver, wander, wander 
Worries, shreds, emotions
indignant 
trace their paths 
build, swell, rise
up
pull, tug, drag
without ceasing 
no 
abandoning, letting go, releasing
letting out!

Pause 
break, bind, bundle 
in images, words, melodies 
freely
shape | create | be.

Chronically creative" height="3638" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a1eb591e558f.jpg" width="2752"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 10:51:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>城市绿意</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1eb262931b8</link><description>&lt;p&gt;城市绿地。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Vegetation, including  daisy blossoms in front, and a building wall, grey, featuring two windows, in the back." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a1eb262931b8.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 10:37:24 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>意大利</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1eaf4b06b10</link><description>&lt;p&gt;意大利&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🇮🇹 " height="1024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/gianpaolofontani/6a1eaf4b06b10.png" width="1536"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://gianpaolofontani.some.pics"&gt;@gianpaolofontani&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 10:24:14 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>